Package com.facebook.buck.test.selectors

Interface TestSelector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PatternTestSelector, SimpleTestSelector
    public interface TestSelector
    A way of matching a test-method in a test-class, and saying whether or not to include any matches in a test run.

      • matches

        boolean matches​(TestDescription description)
        Whether this TestSelector matches the given TestDescription. A class or method name being null in the TestDescription means that it will match anything.
        Parameters:
        description - the TestDescription to match
        Returns:
        true if this selector matches the given TestDescription
